{"tid":395000,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[WOW左十年] The Mist","createTime":"2017-09-10T12:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T12:21:31.000Z","uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cade79385450cd76dc92d580fd8f29b862845e9b","tid":395000,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:30:40.000Z","msg":"記得N年前係舊登有人推介, 拖到今日先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好明最後即係點?<br />\n主角一行人自殺前見到隻大怪物, 所以絕望到自殺<br />\n但係落車之後就見到D軍人救緊人<br />\n照道理咁大隻野唔會轉個頭冇左掛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住SEARCH過下以前D人討論過, 話其實係冇怪物, 只係D人FF<br />\n其實即係點? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb0493cd2f72297fe6b67cd814c768e517efcd7","tid":395000,"uid":12933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"請問邊度有得睇番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129327f5eb93fa60f17ebda71adcdb4d1269a408","tid":395000,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"姐係主角只要忍多陣唔出去<br />\n所有人都唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為軍人已經入緊黎<br />\n留係超市個班仆街<br />\neg教會女人全部唔使死"},{"pid":"dc57ddb05c65e0cbfdd086580f0d8644b2b0541d","tid":395000,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係主角只要忍多陣唔出去<br />\n所有人都唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為軍人已經入緊黎<br />\n留係超市個班仆街<br />\neg教會女人全部唔使死</blockquote><br />\n咁作者想表達乜野 成日一諗起就覺得男主好慘"},{"pid":"0591b407a30d71ebf9a4982a5c637e1078cf6d11","tid":395000,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T12:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐係主角只要忍多陣唔出去<br />\n所有人都唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為軍人已經入緊黎<br />\n留係超市個班仆街<br />\neg教會女人全部唔使死</blockquote><br />\n咁作者想表達乜野 成日一諗起就覺得男主好慘</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係想串下英雄主義係咪真係好<br />\n我地睇開的戲黎講<br />\n好似主角咁勇的人最後都會嬴<br />\n但現實可能唔係咁<br />\n仆街自私的人係會笑到最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0c771c02ce5f4125b226a5b7748b244bb88fc5","tid":395000,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係主角只要忍多陣唔出去<br />\n所有人都唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為軍人已經入緊黎<br />\n留係超市個班仆街<br />\neg教會女人全部唔使死</blockquote><br />\n我想知既係最後山咁大果隻怪物係咪真係存在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd45dfeb71b9906ed84f698fe7c026f3443491d2","tid":395000,"uid":55192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐係主角只要忍多陣唔出去<br />\n所有人都唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為軍人已經入緊黎<br />\n留係超市個班仆街<br />\neg教會女人全部唔使死</blockquote><br />\n我想知既係最後山咁大果隻怪物係咪真係存在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係真係存在 <br />\n<br />\n我估佢講緊人睇野其實好窄 將自己眼前嘅問題放到無限大<br />\n眼前出現怪物 大家就覺得世界末日 <br />\n<br />\n只有勇於離開框框嘅人<br />\n行出去睇下個世界<br />\n就會發現 根本世界未末日 <br />\n解決方法唔係冇 <br />\n只係人鑽牛角尖 唔肯行出去 <br />\n<br />\n我估apply晒落大部份身邊嘅事件都適用"},{"pid":"8d5f4d47b790e5eac18acd3031f429e2a59be928","tid":395000,"uid":86,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T13:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>姐係主角只要忍多陣唔出去<br />\n所有人都唔使死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為軍人已經入緊黎<br />\n留係超市個班仆街<br />\neg教會女人全部唔使死</blockquote><br />\n我想知既係最後山咁大果隻怪物係咪真係存在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係真係存在 <br />\n<br />\n我估佢講緊人睇野其實好窄 將自己眼前嘅問題放到無限大<br />\n眼前出現怪物 大家就覺得世界末日 <br />\n<br />\n只有勇於離開框框嘅人<br />\n行出去睇下個世界<br />\n就會發現 根本世界未末日 <br />\n解決方法唔係冇 <br />\n只係人鑽牛角尖 唔肯行出去 <br />\n<br />\n我估apply晒落大部份身邊嘅事件都適用</blockquote><br />\n行岀去 <br />\n有個警察咪行左<br />\n佢地仲搵到條屍？<br />\n<br />\n超級市場入面<br />\n先有羊群心理 有個講故事叻少少嘅人<br />\n就可以控制到大部分人<br />\n<br />\n只有個心堅定少少<br />\n先可以獨立思考到<br />\n<br />\n最後可能曲線想講<br />\n未去到最後真係唔好放棄<br />\n有危就有機<br />\n是危是機要最後一刻先知"},{"pid":"adc4b49a408333a8eccee1371c741dfcedbefca0","tid":395000,"uid":130349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"而家有冇睇新個套"},{"pid":"229c6f362adc777251bc5fb64547f870e55093a6","tid":395000,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T14:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家有冇睇新個套</blockquote><br />\n冇睇啊, 好少追劇, 追呢個動作好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw, 好唔好睇? 同埋咩網會有得追? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連walking dead都未睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 